iner and client command\nwords are unnecessarily verbose. UG documents list as clearing trainer\nGUI selection, but ListCommand does not call clearSelectedTrainer().\n\nLet\u0027s,\n* add parseCalorieTarget() to accept 0 as a valid calorie target value\n* update SetCalorieTargetCommand to treat cal/0 as a clear operation\n* fix log-calorie overflow error to a user-friendly message\n* rename add-trainer, edit-trainer to add-t, edit-t\n* rename add-client, edit-client, reassign-client to add-c, edit-c,\n  reassign-c\n* correct UG list command description to match actual code behavior\n* update all UG and DG references to reflect renamed commands\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":30,"deletions":13},"docs":{"insertions":62,"deletions":58},"test-code":{"insertions":4,"deletions":4}}},{"hash":"cd19811cdaacdd4062feef618037ef1c95f741ba","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #265 from ephtale/ped","messageBody":"Address PE-D issues","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-04-13T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"2caea88b0b936acf5026d2b814767cf6c62ebe9e","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #269 from ephtale/uifix","messageBody":"Fix #253","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"eadb10a5af909dccfd386c9b469df44ee9a6b779","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Authorship: remove tags causing misattribution of teammates\u0027 code","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":0,"deletions":6}}},{"hash":"774d733e59b20198dabf584bea178e4cb74a10d2","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Revert \"Authorship: remove tags causing misattribution of teammates\u0027 code\"","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":6,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"eccf823b958444eaf37eec7a4bf83815a2d88e68","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #275 from prithvibhardwaj/2101-ug","messageBody":"Edit UG according to suggestions given in CS2101",