d all parser tests to use new c/ format\n- Updated AddressBookParserTest integration tests\n- Updated HelpWindow command summary\n- Updated UserGuide format lines, examples, and command summary table\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":35,"deletions":23},"docs":{"insertions":12,"deletions":12},"test-code":{"insertions":22,"deletions":19}}},{"hash":"1d9be105350b74d55cedd22fbd8e416ba8a0c9e4","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Shorten command names: set-calorie-target → set-cal, log-calorie → log-cal","messageBody":"Reduces typing friction for high-frequency daily commands.\nCOMMAND_WORD change propagates automatically to MESSAGE_USAGE,\nAddressBookParser, and all test files using the constant.\n\nAlso updated hardcoded strings in:\n- HelpCommand.java\n- HelpWindow.java\n- UserGuide.md (TOC, headings, format lines, examples, FAQ, table)\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":6,"deletions":6},"docs":{"insertions":11,"deletions":11}}},{"hash":"b06c78a11f438de8ea3cfee7c7d06a2e42c88c03","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #261 from TheSputnikSpacecraft/MoreBugFixes","messageBody":"Fix calorie commands, shorten command words, and sync docs to code","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-04-13T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"2f786c7442d08d43d2d4e2ada06f7758d1c178cc","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #270 from TheSputnikSpacecraft/FixAuthorship","messageBody":"Authorship: remove tags causing misattribution of teammates\u0027 code","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"ff0cbf9cea45a826e145a8cbfaf4e5d3c762dae6","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #271 from AY2526S2-CS2103T-T17-1/revert-270-FixAuthorship","messageBody":"Revert \"Authorship: remove tags causing misattribution of teammates\u0027 code\"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"1d85c2ba7d0f11cd972bf44608c920cdac21f25e","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add @@author tags